<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar-content">
        <div class="navbar__right">
            <div class="navbar__logo">
                <img src="/image/logo.png" alt="Logo">
            </div>
            <div class="navbar__links">
              <div class="navigation-links">
                <a href="/" class="navbar__link">Home</a>
                <a href="/add-project" class="navbar__link">My Project</a>
              </div>
                <a href="/contact"><button class="navbar__button__contact">Contact Me</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar__left">
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="icon" onclick="myFunction()">
                  <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="card-image">
        <div class="card-image__hello">
            <p class="card-image__hello__emoji">ðŸ‘‹</p>
            <div class="card-image__hello__text">
                <p>Hello World!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-image__detail-project">
            <div class="card-image__container-text">
                <h2><u>Get to Know Me.</u></h2>
                <p>
                    Hello! I'm , Farhan Muzaki, a passionate <span class="circle-sketch-highlight">Front-End Developer</span> with a keen eye for design and <span class="circle-sketch-highlight">  UI/UX </span>. I blend
                    creativity with code to craft visually stunning and user-friendly web experiences. Let's create
                    something amazing together!
                </p>
                <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ut, tempora! Cum ullam quis ipsam nam labore, aut optio provident harum aspernatur aliquam tempore ex error accusantium sed eos iste qui.
                </p>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Laborum velit voluptates voluptatem, nulla est deleniti maxime nobis architecto nostrum dicta fugit error alias iste vel tempora obcaecati quo dolores sunt.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-image__cta-button">
                <a href="contact.html" class="contact-link">Contact</a>
                <a href="" class="download-link">Download CV <i class="fa-regular fa-download"></i
                ></a>
              </div>
            <div class="card-image__icon-social">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-square-instagram"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-square-twitter"></i>
                <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-image_profile">
            <div class="card-image_profile-image">
                <img src="/image/profile.jpg" alt=" "/>
            </div>
            <div class="card-image_profile-detail">
                <h2>Farhan Muzaki</h2>
                <p>Front-End Developer</p>
              </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center py-3 px-4 ">
        <h1>My Projects</h1>
        <a href="/add-project" class="btn btn-primary mb-3">Add New Project</a>
    </div>
        {{#if projects.length}}
        <div class="col-md-4 cardProject-container mb-4">
                
              </div>
            <ul class="list-group">
                {{#each projects}}
                <div class="card shadow-sm " style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;" >
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="mb-1">{{name}}</h5>
                        <p class="mb-1">Start Date: {{startDate}}</p>
                        <p class="mb-1">End Date: {{endDate}}</p>
                        <small>Description: {{description}}</small>
                    <a href="/project/{{id}}" class="btn btn-dark mt-2 w-100">View Details</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>
        {{else}}
        <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center m-5 flex-column">
            <img src="/image/not-found.png" alt="" style="width: 300px; align-self: center">
            <p class="text-center w-100">No projects found</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>
</body>
</html>
